Author: hhheath <heath@steppe.sh>
Date:   Tue Apr 7 20:05:12 2026 -0500

    fix: address codebase review findings across security, correctness, and performance

    - Fix broken database transactions (execute on tx, not self.conn)
    - Fix panic on endpoint removal when vec becomes empty
    - Add HTTP connect/request timeouts to prevent indefinite hangs
    - Check stream buffer size before extending to prevent overshoot
    - Sanitize API error messages to avoid leaking credentials in UI
    - Set 0700 permissions on config/data directories (Unix)
    - Remove hot-path .clone() calls in per-frame UI iteration loops
    - Add StreamEvent::ModelsLoaded variant instead of JSON smuggling
    - Clear search results when query is emptied
    - Replace font family HashMap unwraps with defensive if-let checks
    - Remove redundant double-clone of base_url
    - Return iterator from newline_positions instead of allocating Vec
    - Extract ChatParams struct to fix clippy too_many_arguments lint
    - Collapse nested if per clippy suggestion

    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
    Entire-Checkpoint: f38e1d4716af

